<div class="title">Out of Nowhere, I Lost My Mind</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=ks&Exact=1">ks</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; ks. "Out of Nowhere, I Lost My Mind: An Experience with AMT (exp38423)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 24, 2004. erowid.org/exp/38423</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

<!-- DoseChart -->
	<table border='2' cellpadding='4' cellspacing='0' bordercolor='#224422' class='dosechart'>
